Global Portable Cool-mist Humidifiers Market Insights
Portable Cool-mist Humidifiers Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.4% from 2024 to 2030.

Portable Cool-mist Humidifiers Market Overview
The global Portable Cool-mist Humidifiers market has seen substantial growth over the years, with a market value of USD 1.5 billion in 2024 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 billion by 2030, registering a CAGR of 8.1% during the forecast period. This market's expansion is primarily driven by the rising demand for healthy indoor air quality, particularly in regions with dry climates and during colder seasons. The increasing awareness of respiratory diseases and the adverse effects of dry air on health has fueled the demand for cool-mist humidifiers. The market is also benefitting from growing technological advancements in product features such as smart humidifiers with IoT connectivity and energy-efficient designs.

